</paragraph>
<newline />
<paragraph>
    <chunk style="font-family:Times;font-weight:bold;">BORROWER details: </chunk>
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
    <chunk style="font-family:Times;">Name: @Model.PersonalData.FirstName @Model.PersonalData.LastName</chunk>
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
    <chunk style="font-family:Times;">Personal number: @Model.PersonalData.Identification</chunk>
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
    <chunk style="font-family:Times;">Address: @Model.PersonalData.Address</chunk>
</paragraph>
<newline />
<paragraph>
    <chunk style="font-family:Times;font-weight:bold;">LOAN details: </chunk>
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
    <chunk style="font-family:Times;">Name: @Model.LoanAmount @Model.Currency</chunk>
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
    <chunk style="font-family:Times;">Tariff: @Model.Tariff.Name</chunk>
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
    <chunk style="font-family:Times;">Tariff: @(Model.Tariff.InterestRate * 100)%</chunk>
</paragraph>

<newline />

<paragraph>
    <chunk style="font-family:Times;font-weight:bold;">Terms and conditions: </chunk>
</paragraph>
<newline />
<list numbered="true" symbolindent="15" font="unknown">
    <listitem leading="18.0" font="Times" size="12.0" align="Default" indentationleft="15.0">
        <chunk font="Times" size="12.0">The LENDER agrees to offer a loan of the above said amount to the BORROWER on the condition that the BORROWER must not delay the repayment after end of contract.</chunk>
    </listitem>
    <listitem leading="18.0" font="Times" size="12.0" align="Default" indentationleft="15.0">
        <chunk font="Times" size="12.0">The BORROWER must not use the loan money for any illegal activity or purchase.</chunk>
    </listitem>
    <listitem leading="18.0" font="Times" size="12.0" align="Default" indentationleft="15.0">
        <chunk font="Times" size="12.0">If the BORROWER is not paying his payments in time, The LENDER will fine him. Every day of overdue tax is accrued. It is calculated by doubled loan tariff interest rate from current sum of general debt and interest balance.</chunk>
    </listitem>
</list>
